data.name: sqlSelectCommand1.CommandText
data.value: SELECT hold_hist_id, hold_id, proj_lot_id, pri_id, case when priority = 'P' then 'Primary' else 'Secondary' end [priority], start_date, end_date, s.Lot_Status, sl.Sub_Status, pt.PurchaserType, c.NAME, phone_num, price_quoted, trans_date, username, comments, Confirmed FROM PROJ_LOT_HOLD_HIST h join LD_Lot_Status s on s.Lot_Status_ID=h.lot_status_id join LD_Sub_Lot_Status sl on sl.Sub_Status_ID=h.sub_status_id join LD_Purchaser_Type pt on pt.LD_Purchaser_Type_ID=h.purchaser_type_id join CUSTOMERS c on c.CUSTOMER_ID=h.purchaser_id WHERE proj_lot_id = @proj_lot_id order by hold_id desc
